        <updateDate>2019-03-20T15:09:55Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Combating Opioid Misuse By Advancing Treatment Act of 2018 or the COMBAT Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Government Accountability Office to conduct a study on best practices&nbsp;used by federal departments and agencies to reduce opioid use following a medical procedure that is conducted, funded, or otherwise supported by such agencies and departments.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
